<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạlkl ymḍy̱ wyzwl lạ sẖyʾ ybqy̱ lạ yḥwl
 lạ ybqy̱ ʿsẖb fy ạlḥqwl wạlzhr ạ̉yḍạaⁿ lldẖbwl
 yạrby ạ̉nt wḥdk tbqy̱ wklhạ tbyd
 lạ dwrạn wlạ tgẖyyr fyk yạ sydy ạlmjyd

[V2]
 2- yạ sydy lys swạk fạ̉nt tbqy̱ fy ʿlạk
 kmạ bạlạ̉ms lạ tzạl tgẖyyrk mn ạlmḥạl
 lwlạk ạ̉mḍy fy ḍyạʿ ky ạ̉nthy ạ̹ly̱ ḍyạʿ
 sẖkrạaⁿ lk fạ̉nt ly ạ̹ny lk rby ạlʿly

[V3]
 3- ṣdyqy ymḍy wạljfạ qd sạd mn bʿd ạlwfạ
 wfạʾh kạn wfạʾ ạlận ṣạr kạlhbạʾ
 lknk rb ạlsmạ ạ̉wfy̱ mn kl ạlạ̉ṣdqạʾ
 ffy yswʿ ạlạ̉lzq mn ạ̹kẖwty ly ạlʿzạʾ

[V4]
 4- ạlʿmr ymḍy wyzwl mtẖl bkẖạr lạ ykwn
 tmḍy ạlạ̉yạm wạlsnwn tmḍy tṭyr lạ tkwn
 lkn fy hdẖạ ly ạlʿzạʾ fhw yqrb ạlsmạʾ
 ywmạaⁿ syạ̉ty bạlbhạʾ mạ ạ̉bhj ywm ạllqạʾ</lyrics>
